{"tid":1321990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再買War game裝備去打怪!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-15T22:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:14.000Z","uid":241868,"like":317,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"84dd42c657e7380a78203723c82eeb4e4db4d36f","tid":1321990,"uid":241868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T22:55:01.000Z","msg":"各位義士，唔好再去課金買或者帶自己War game既裝備去打怪<br />\n都請某啲人拍宣傳片同出去既時候，唔好再著到打war game咁<br />\n以下我解釋點解:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.只係玩具</span></strong></span><br />\n唔好再比人利用黎做賺錢工具，我見過有啲賣war game野既店做宣傳叫人去買&quot;更好既裝備，裝備自己&quot;<br />\n大佬呀，個個只係玩具only，只有5mm厚度，內膽又冇吸震功能，比啲怪一打就會破防<br />\n地盤/單車頭效果一定比war game頭盔好幾十倍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2.唔係真既頭盔就一定有用</strong></span></span><br />\n唔係所有軍用既頭盔都有防撞既功能，大多數只係用黎防破片，阻擋細小/尖銳既物體，並將佢彈開<br />\n並唔係用黎擋撞擊/鈍物攻擊，因為內膽唔似單車頭盔個種可以防撞吸震，所以你中左你就會腦震盪暈低<br />\n要有防撞吸震功能，唔該你去買真既防暴頭盔或者OPS Core，呢一類真係有防撞吸震功能既頭盔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3.war game風鏡係冇撚用架</strong></span></span><br />\nwar game玩具風鏡透氣、唔防彈、易起霧，你帶黎做咩撚野????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n市面上好多聲稱防彈既風鏡/眼鏡、都只係用黎擋用黎打雀既bird shot，連9mm都擋唔到，布袋彈打中，一樣穿，到時連碎片入你眼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4.吸仇恨</strong></span></span><br />\n你係黎呢度扮型想上鏡定係點?你著到咁，係我都打你先啦!<br />\n當你身邊個個地盤頭盔既時候，得你一個著到標怪立異咁，唔打你先打邊個先????<br />\n就好似你平時打機咁，你會集火打特別怪先，定係打兵仔先?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯一值得買既，只係vest，同放入vest既軟墊</span></strong></span><br />\nvest款愈低調愈好，但軟墊防禦力期望唔好太高，因為佢唔厚，仲軟過軟墊地毯<br />\n原因我再重申一次: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為佢只係一樣用黎打war game既玩具</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"327317d6cf3eb140c6e45202e35e11d238765e73","tid":1321990,"uid":241868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac8a5647aba2c93564a920a933681654664fc5bb","tid":1321990,"uid":241868,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:08:02.000Z","msg":"推呀!! dislike個2個打war game打上腦?想比狗集火打先? 定還是你係war game店做 怕比我影響到生意?"},{"pid":"7212b67c724c9e3f7c0417c3e95143bd6b8e0d7d","tid":1321990,"uid":241868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:23:01.000Z","msg":"推! 比更多人睇到 買返啲真正實用既裝備"},{"pid":"e654c67210922656eda497830942c141392a2460","tid":1321990,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7e9b21f00abcf1f85b5615c51e82749ae938ed2","tid":1321990,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個刻骨銘心既夢，想同大家分享一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321643</a>"},{"pid":"316c6a3b7bc486fdd76130df6faae63d05a11dab","tid":1321990,"uid":35632,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:29:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56dbe3c56c27ec4553e897aa7e559d0734621b9","tid":1321990,"uid":174120,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n 不過有手足鍾意既話就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係加強自己心理"},{"pid":"70fab48e88928a38739ff78821e499e48540762a","tid":1321990,"uid":128430,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"用消防頭盔都好過用war game頭盔"},{"pid":"7ffdd8eb49f4183b33903130962452e00806860f","tid":1321990,"uid":25468,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"以前油麻地有二手真正軍隊裝備賣 , 之前鴨記都見到有檔賣類似野"},{"pid":"d265604f59d13fb983f7ca749caf2cbf6196019c","tid":1321990,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:33:3